The paper discusses online learning algorithms for prediction problems, including classification and regression. This falls under the category of machine learning, which is typically classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) in arXiv. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of regularizers, which is a common technique in optimization and can be classified under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the design and analysis of algorithms, which can be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
